2) cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely, as the paper deals with AER cameras and object classification. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category, as the paper proposes a novel learning algorithm for AER object classification. 
4) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible, as the paper deals with a biologically plausible and energy-efficient approach to object classification. 
5) cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still possible, as AER cameras and SNNs are relevant to robotics applications.
